OL,3,CI am not afraid to take on vested
OL,4,Cinterests, Swinney to say
OL,6,FScotland's First Minister is expected
OL,7,Fto tell trade unionists he is "not
OL,8,Fafraid of taking on vested interests"
OL,9,Fin a speech on Tuesday after he
OL,10,Fproposed plans to cap food prices.
OL,12,FAnnouncing the SNP's manifesto last
OL,13,Fweek, John Swinney said an SNP
OL,14,Fgovernment elected after May 7 would
OL,15,Fput a ceiling on up to 50 essential
OL,16,Fitems.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
