OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776746255
OL,3,CI am not afraid to take on vested
OL,4,Cinterests, Swinney to say
OL,6,FThe plan was immediately criticised by
OL,7,Fthe industry and the UK Government `
OL,8,Fwho suggested it could cost "millions"
OL,9,Fin legal fees if retail giants take
OL,10,Faction.
OL,12,FIn an address to the STUC Congress,
OL,13,Fthe First Minister will suggest he is
OL,14,Fup for the fight.
OL,16,FThe First Minister is expected to say:
OL,17,F"As First Minister, when it comes to
OL,18,Fhelping people with the cost of
OL,19,Fliving, I am not afraid to take on
OL,20,Fvested interests.
OL,26,@pD@]OUpD@fO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776746255
OL,3,CI am not afraid to take on vested
OL,4,Cinterests, Swinney to say
OL,6,F"I know just how unaffordable food is
OL,7,Ffor too many people ` and it is
OL,8,Fimpacting on health and nutrition.
OL,10,F"That's why I will use public health
OL,11,Fpowers to introduce a maximum price
OL,12,Ffor essential food items.
OL,14,F"There are some who have criticised
OL,15,Fthis policy. But, congress, we will
OL,16,Ftake forward fair food pricing because
OL,17,Fit is the right thing to do. I believe
OL,18,Fit will be transformational.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
