OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776746255
OL,3,CI am not afraid to take on vested
OL,4,Cinterests, Swinney to say
OL,6,F"In these tough times, that is the
OL,7,Fsort of bold vision that you should
OL,8,Frightly expect from your government."
OL,10,FHe will also take aim at Reform UK,
OL,11,Fits leader Nigel Farage and his
OL,12,F"cronies in Scotland".
OL,14,F"You know that the rise of the far
OL,15,Fright has been a top concern of mine
OL,16,Fsince I took office. If I am re-
OL,17,Felected, I promise that I will not let
OL,18,Fup on this fight," he will tell
OL,19,Fdelegates.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@eO]tD@AOUtD@UO]vD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
