CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776746255
OL,3,CI am not afraid to take on vested
OL,4,Cinterests, Swinney to say
OL,6,F"My government will continue working
OL,7,Fto build a Scotland where everyone's
OL,8,Frights are respected ` and where every
OL,9,Fperson is given the chance to make
OL,10,Ftheir contribution to Scotland's story.
OL,12,F"Be in no doubt ` when it comes to
OL,13,FReform UK, I will have absolutely no
OL,14,Ftruck with Nigel Farage or his cronies
OL,15,Fin Scotland.
OL,17,F"There will be no grubby deals. No
OL,18,Fbackroom conversations.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
